ATTRIBUTION

This LoRA adapter is trained on top of ResembleAI Chatterbox Multilingual
(MIT License, https://github.com/resemble-ai/chatterbox). Users deploying
this adapter must honour Chatterbox's MIT attribution requirements in
addition to the Apache-2.0 terms above. The Chatterbox base model is not
included in this release; users obtain it directly from Resemble AI.

Training data is drawn from publicly released Indic speech corpora
(IndicTTS, Rasa, FLEURS, Shrutilipi subsets) under their respective
CC-BY-4.0-compatible licences. Attribution to the data providers is the
responsibility of end-users who redistribute downstream works.
